    filter(State == "QLD" | State == "NT" | State == "VIC" | State == "TAS") %>%

    mutate(Trips = sum(Trips)) %>%

    ggplot(aes(quarter(Quarter), Trips, color = year(Quarter))) +
    geom_path() +
